Wine Project FastAPI

How to run

1. create and activate a virtualenv
   python -m venv venv
   source venv/bin/activate

2. install requirements
   pip install -r requirements.txt

3. start the app
   uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8000

4. Open docs
   http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

Run tests
   pytest -q

